title: Au Lac - Fountain Valley
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Chinese, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out, Vietnamese
description: Vegan restaurant operating since 1997 under the direction of Chef Ito. Has a second location in Downtown LA. Offers "Humanese cuisine" comprising of Vietnamese and Chinese vegan cuisine with a variety of mock meats and brown rice available, as well as a separate raw food menu. Extensive beverages, teas, elixirs and shots menu. Parking lot on-site.
